Afternoon beach at low tide. Crazy zoomies again and she - for the first time ever- ran into the water knee deep to chase the housemate who was swimming! A once off but is definitely less scared of water now.
Then found a fish skeleton and ate it ?? https://t.co/yGRVVGP73d
